    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在疯子路易十六国王和其残暴的巧工机器人军团侵袭之下，城市燃烧殆尽，尸横遍野。埃癸斯，一个由工程师沃康松打造好成为皇后保镖的机械杰作，必须在这款极具挑战的动作角色扮演游戏中拯救法国大革命。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>与巧工机器人之间的艰难战斗</strong></h2></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1283400/extras/20d45a4b5ea1c26306b311fdd3c2b906.poster.avif?t=1764149288\" width=614 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1283400/extras/20d45a4b5ea1c26306b311fdd3c2b906.webm?t=1764149288\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1283400/extras/20d45a4b5ea1c26306b311fdd3c2b906.mp4?t=1764149288\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >要想对抗国王的机械士兵，必须要有致命的准确度。使出行云流水般的闪避、招架和跳跃，在巴黎杀出一条血路。每场战斗都会考验你的胆量，且要有出色的驾驭能力，在面对巨大无情的机器首领同时更需要耐心与技巧。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>埃癸斯：有着超凡技艺的角色</strong></h2></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1283400/extras/be5734aa4f437961e50a487949b1b0ca.poster.avif?t=1764149288\" width=614 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1283400/extras/be5734aa4f437961e50a487949b1b0ca.webm?t=1764149288\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1283400/extras/be5734aa4f437961e50a487949b1b0ca.mp4?t=1764149288\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着游戏的推进，定义自己专属的游戏风格及升级你的能力。你可以选择扮演残忍无情的战士、强硬打击的保镖、见血封喉的舞者或者深谙元素技艺的大师。在每一场战斗中利用种类繁多的武器和技巧以呈现自己独特的战斗方式。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>革命性的巴黎便是你的舞台</strong></h2></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1283400/extras/658a508eb5bba55b793e318d484dd579.poster.avif?t=1764149288\" width=614 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1283400/extras/658a508eb5bba55b793e318d484dd579.webm?t=1764149288\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1283400/extras/658a508eb5bba55b793e318d484dd579.mp4?t=1764149288\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >利用你前进道路上所发现的马车、抓钩、秘密通道、详细地图和其它方法和工具，探索这座历经最黑暗时光的城市。你的抓钩会为探索和巴黎的垂直度增添新的维度。结合你的冲锋能力，它让你能在多个层次的反复探索中了解城市的所有秘密。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>改变历史进程</strong></h2></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1283400/extras/ccc0efb36ad78e4798cbfb3d7fd11f66.poster.avif?t=1764149288\" width=614 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1283400/extras/ccc0efb36ad78e4798cbfb3d7fd11f66.webm?t=1764149288\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1283400/extras/ccc0efb36ad78e4798cbfb3d7fd11f66.mp4?t=1764149288\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你是这场架空历史的主要角色之一，在这段历史中，暴君正在扼杀巴黎。在这一路上会遇到盟友和意图不明的敌人，像是玛丽-安托瓦内特、拉法耶特和罗伯斯庇尔。由你来斩断所有阴谋，终结个人疯狂，引领法国大革命走向成功。</p>",
